        切換巡覽列或頁籤巡覽的下拉選單。
        <!--Toggles the dropdown menu of a given navbar or tabbed navigation.-->
    </p>

  <h3>事件<!--Events--></h3>
    <p>
        所有下拉選單事件都會在 <code>.dropdown-menu</code> 的父元素被觸發。
        <!--All dropdown events are fired at the <code>.dropdown-menu</code>'s parent element.-->
    </p>
  <div class="table-responsive">
    <table class="table table-bordered table-striped">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th style="width: 150px;">事件型別<!--Event Type--></th>
          <th>說明<!--Description--></th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>show.bs.dropdown</td>
            <td>
                當顯示執行體個方法被呼叫，此事件會立即被觸發。切換的連結元素可作為事件的 <code>relatedTarget</code> 屬性來使用。
                <!--This event fires immediately when the show instance method is called. The toggling anchor element is available as the <code>relatedTarget</code> property of the event.-->
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>shown.bs.dropdown</td>
            <td>
                當下拉選單已經在使用者面前顯示完成（且 CSS 轉場效果已經完成），此事件會立即被觸發。切換的連結元素可作為事件的 <code>relatedTarget</code> 屬性來使用。
                <!--This event is fired when the dropdown has been made visible to the user (will wait for CSS transitions, to complete).  The toggling anchor element is available as the <code>relatedTarget</code> property of the event.-->
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>hide.bs.dropdown</td>
            <td>
                當隱藏執行體個方法被呼叫，此事件會立即被觸發。切換的連結元素可作為事件的 <code>relatedTarget</code> 屬性來使用。
                <!--This event is fired immediately when the hide instance method has been called. The toggling anchor element is available as the <code>relatedTarget</code> property of the event.-->
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>hidden.bs.dropdown</td>
            <td>
                當下拉選單已經在使用者面前隱藏完成（且 CSS 轉場效果已經完成），此事件會立即被觸發。切換的連結元素可作為事件的 <code>relatedTarget</code> 屬性來使用。
                <!--This event is fired when the dropdown has finished being hidden from the user (will wait for CSS transitions, to complete). The toggling anchor element is available as the <code>relatedTarget</code> property of the event.-->
            </td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
